{"tid":1134734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保釣行動遊行 要求日本德仁天皇特赦郭紹傑嚴敏華","createTime":"2019-05-02T00:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T04:56:48.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f927528772ab52d234da2f261a249413b922d27f","tid":1134734,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:59:54.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】保釣行動委員會遊行抗議，要求日本政府釋放在當地還柙的郭紹傑和嚴敏華。<br />\n<br />\n委員會成員由中環郵政局出發，遊行至日本領事館。他們要求剛即位的日本德仁天皇作出特赦。<br />\n<br />\n郭紹傑去年趁南京大屠殺81周年前夕，在東京靖國神社外焚燒東條英機的道具神主牌，當場被捕，嚴敏華在場攝錄過程。<br />\n<br />\n兩人被日本當局起訴非法進入他人建築物罪，在當地一直被扣押，等候法庭完成審理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/保釣行動遊行要求日本釋放郭紹傑嚴敏華-054655109.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%A3%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%87%8B%E6%94%BE%E9%83%AD%E7%B4%B9%E5%82%91%E5%9A%B4%E6%95%8F%E8%8F%AF-054655109.html&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=f3b61028\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/保釣行動遊行要求日本釋放郭紹傑嚴敏華-054655109.html</a>"},{"pid":"799b639cf21adcdfc642707c7ca84d38f195be77","tid":1134734,"uid":17641,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:03:56.000Z","msg":"好心俾啲骨氣，要殺悉隨尊便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d13dfd209e93739808be29a56b2a3af5ee5829f","tid":1134734,"uid":51701,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:36:52.000Z","msg":"企開啲啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"6ce36a6b1fa2bda751e59c9d4bc9107c93817f23","tid":1134734,"uid":167933,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:38:24.000Z","msg":"好醜怪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要威又要求人放過佢"},{"pid":"cb23b3ae248ff8511bb983e0a14d71c7c5eb4063","tid":1134734,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:38:52.000Z","msg":"為國捐軀 死也幸福"},{"pid":"3b539c996e16b518d5b32